<P>
SAN DIEGO SPORTS ET CETERA: BASEBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
John Gibbs relieved Kevin Nielsen in the fifth inning and went the rest of the 
way to improve to 2-0 as visiting San Diego State upset 14th-ranked Long Beach 
State, 8-5. 
</P>
<P>
The Aztecs (21-13) got three RBIs from Eric Christofferson and two more from 
Brian Dunn. Long Beach State is now 29-7. 
</P>
