point above Hollywood. CON KEYES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Max Almedo, above 
left, front man for a Santa Ana chicken shop, sweats through one of hottest 
jobs in town. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, West Los Angeles 
temperature sign registers 107 as record heat drives thousands to area beaches. 
GEORGE R. FRY / Los Angeles Times; ELLEN JASKOL / Los Angeles Times 
