white. ; Photo, All-white look is new for GE's popular Spacemaker 
refrigerator/freezer, left. Black &amp; Decker's Thermal Carafe Coffee Maker, 
right, now comes in 4-cup version. ; Photo, Black &amp; Decker's thermal carafe 
coffeemaker now comes in personalized 4-cup version. 
</P>
