<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Kerman Maddox led a recall effort against Robert Farrell in the 8th City 
Council District in 1988. A story in Thursday's editions incorrectly stated 
that Maddox had been a candidate for the council seat. 
</P>
