arraignment where he pleaded not guilty to conspiracy to commit assault. ; 
Photo, Pilar Wayne, mother of Aissa and widow of John Wayne, listens in court 
on Wednesday. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
