9-mm. semiautomatic pistol. Officers provide their own weapons. 
</P>
<P>
Patrol car: Remington 870 shotgun. 
</P>
<P>
Special unit: Sawed-off shotguns; Heckler &amp; Koch MP-5 rifles; AR-15 assault 
rifles; Benelli Super-90 M-1 12-gauge shotguns. 
</P>
